  <brief_title>Diagnosis of Coronary Artery Disease in High Risk Diabetic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Diagnosis of Coronary Artery Disease in High Risk Diabetic Patients :Comparison Between Stress Echocardiography and Stress Scintigraphy in the Detection of Silent Myocardial Ischemia</official_title>
